{"tid":389417,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] Come On James!! 九寨溝何來失禮?","createTime":"2017-09-06T08:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T04:03:03.000Z","uid":45011,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d220304d566280b75de317695128d2b9dc6377e2","tid":389417,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:53:32.000Z","msg":"直接上Blog睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://aamusictravel.com/2016/09/01/come-on-james-%E4%B9%9D%E5%AF%A8%E6%BA%9D%E4%BD%95%E4%BE%86%E5%A4%B1%E7%A6%AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamusictravel.com%2F2016%2F09%2F01%2Fcome-on-james-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25AF%25A8%25E6%25BA%259D%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E7%25A6%25AE%2F&d=cjmf4A%2BpYGFx723OlEA3xRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=9759d9c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://aamusictravel.com/2016/09/01/come-on-james-%E4%B9%9D%E5%AF%A8%E6%BA%9D%E4%BD%95%E4%BE%86%E5%A4%B1%E7%A6%AE/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陶傑筆下的那個港女，看不起自己那個堅持去九寨溝，不去歐洲的那個男朋友，九寨溝很失禮嗎？ 九寨溝一點也不失禮！<br />\n<br />\n走過成都的熊貓基地，很快便坐飛機到九寨黃龍機場，或簡稱九黃機場，又或稱「十次起飛九次枉」，無論是Arrival還是Departure，delay幾小時算是走運，慘些的，是差不多landing之時被打回頭，我也算是幸運，去程準時，回程早到。不得不提的是，中國空氣污染嚴重人所惜知，四川成都的煙霞相當厲害，當身處客機之中，向外眺望，一層啡黃的污染物頓時在下方，畢竟到了高山，都市的污染和煩囂都被連綿的山脈分隔開了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://aamusictravel.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/img_1961.jpg?w=700\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamusictravel.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F08%2Fimg_1961.jpg%3Fw%3D700&h=e80b1f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了坐飛機不需說delay no more，另一樣走運的是，帶團來說，11月中下旬開始，黃龍封山，也就是說不再需要3點45分morning call那麼辛苦，取而代之的是，可以留在九寨溝久一點，看的東西也自然豐富一點吧。<br />\n<br />\n從機場坐車到九寨溝的入口，沿途是不斷的高山低谷，與及滿途急彎，經過九道拐(這裡剛好有9個髮夾彎)，旅遊車緩緩駛向景區入口，導遊在講解行程，大約個多小時吧，終於到了目的地。<br />\n<br />\n頭一天其實沒什麼特別，只是帶團友到附近的景點走走就回到酒店吃自助餐，僅此而已。放心，戲肉還未到來，下一天的景致，真的叫人嘩然不絕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://aamusictravel.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/img_1963.jpg?w=700\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamusictravel.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F08%2Fimg_1963.jpg%3Fw%3D700&h=0965db2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第2天的早上，我們大約8點左右就到了景區，導遊說這麼早來，一來趁人少，二來趁風細，這樣的話看鏡海就最好。補充一點，在九寨溝你絕對是沒可能靠徒步去所有主要景點的，沿途也是山路之餘，距離往往是以公里計，兩位數字，即使你是「其實唔難」的人，也別忘記這裡海拔也有3000米，行得快一點也有機會高山症發作，所以這裡還是一定要坐環保車，最好是包車那種，不然你坐公共的那種，你一定不夠強國人搶位上車(親身試過)。說回鏡海，可能你會想到天空之鏡，那是不是呢？ 我想，有圖有真相。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://aamusictravel.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/img_19801.jpg?w=700\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamusictravel.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F08%2Fimg_19801.jpg%3Fw%3D700&h=df449cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「嘩!!!」 未下車之時，車內經已嘩聲四起，轉身一看，「鏡海」並非浪得虛名，水面平靜如鏡，眼前天空與群山的倒影也著實令人看不清哪個是真的，哪個是倒影。這次真的很感謝導遊的安排，要拍得如此美景，非靠運氣即成，能夠掌握水面平靜的時間，真的需要靠經驗。事實上，當吃完午飯後再路經此地，鏡海再已非鏡，取而代之的，是朵朵浪花。<br />\n<br />\n除了鏡海之外，其他九寨溝的著名景區如五彩池(不是黃龍的那一個)、火花海、諾日朗瀑布，一樣是「嘩嘩嘩打到黎」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://aamusictravel.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/img_2034.jpg?w=700\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamusictravel.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F08%2Fimg_2034.jpg%3Fw%3D700&h=d1ce9a3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你說，在意大利、法國，你看到這些自然奇觀嗎？<br />\n<br />\n(利申: 去過九寨溝和歐洲)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n===================================================<br />\n<br />\n小弟其他旅遊日記:<br />\n<a href=\"https://aamusictravel.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamusictravel.com&d=cjmf4A%2BpYGFx723OlEA3xRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=af0be57b\" target=\"_blank\">https://aamusictravel.com</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟既Facebook Fans Page:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/aamusictravel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Faamusictravel%2F&d=cjmf4A%2BpYGFx723OlEA3xRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=68f235e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/aamusictravel/</a>"},{"pid":"3a967ead49215a0b27d8a8e99db1fbaec6edfb0c","tid":389417,"uid":120654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:56:21.000Z","msg":"但地震後景觀好像已敗破<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300b131d706190966a94a900f8abfac38c1b85e7","tid":389417,"uid":129829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:58:38.000Z","msg":"可否成熟一點"},{"pid":"76080a9c098a16e97bb3a8be5c9486d8793acad9","tid":389417,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但地震後景觀好像已敗破<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，好多野都風光不再<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee62747f57bb015301a230a89213e5ff3c0a58f","tid":389417,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:00:54.000Z","msg":"第一次去到真係O撚左咀<br />\n<br />\n原來冇p圖<br />\n幾乎0死角<br />\n個個位都咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1c5036f1eb42d5766440139741e3395bca49bf","tid":389417,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:04:11.000Z","msg":"湧現左difference"},{"pid":"bca5cbf95a501a57184d45b78309a64bec7c041c","tid":389417,"uid":120654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:06:47.000Z","msg":"係咪以後都唔洗去"},{"pid":"8db51449f99a364ff8b16da3e9717174dc8c36a1","tid":389417,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"去過克羅地亞16湖，又去過成都九寨溝<br />\n<br />\n九寨溝完勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我睇以前d相，以前冇乜圍欄，少左人工化，應該仲靚。"},{"pid":"86132b51cf0cbdbe7f55cc3029496853cbbd8f82","tid":389417,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:01:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次去到真係O撚左咀<br />\n<br />\n原來冇p圖<br />\n幾乎0死角<br />\n個個位都咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真